Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/fieldville/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Set up NeoBundle
    mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
    git clone git://github.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim ~/.vim/bundle/neobundle.vim

    then Launch vim, run :NeoBundleInstall
